{
  "id": "adv_group_liz_06_05",
  "title": "LizNoir 06 05",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_amepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "america_park",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_05-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、はぁ、はぁ、き、今日のマラソンは\n全員記録更新ですぅ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Pant Pant Pant T-today's marathon was…\na new record for everyone…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_amepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "america_park",
      "startTime": 9.6438100814
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_05-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、はぁ、体を温めるだけのはずだったのに\nどうして、途中から競争に……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Pant Pant We were just supposed to warm up‚\nbut why did it turn into a competition…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_amepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "america_park",
      "startTime": 19.8294331549
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_05-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、はぁ、軽いアップのつもりだったのに……\n莉央が大人げないから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Pant Pant I was just going for a light warm-up…\nRio got way too competitive.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_05-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、はぁ、葵だって\n最後は、全力疾走、だったじゃない……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Pant Pant You too‚ Aoi.\nYou were sprinting at the end…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_amepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "america_park",
      "startTime": 34.6785512922
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_05-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "ふぅ、今日も勝てませんでした\nお二人とも、凄いです……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sigh I couldn't win again today.\nYou two are amazing…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_amepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "america_park",
      "startTime": 42.0731315451
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_05-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、はぁ、こころは可愛らしさでは、全然負けて……\nませんが……先輩達が凄いのは……同意です……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Pant Pant I-I'm not losing at all in terms of cuteness…\nb-but…I agree that senpai are amazing…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_amepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "america_park",
      "startTime": 53.5751953599
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_05-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "何言ってるんだい、凄いのは愛とこころだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What are you talking about? You two are the amazing ones.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.5751953599,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_amepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "america_park",
      "startTime": 58.9507285115
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――え？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.9507285115,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_amepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "america_park",
      "startTime": 60.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_05-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "出会った頃、君達は僕達にまるで\nついてこれなかったじゃないか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When we first met‚ you two couldn't even\nkeep up with us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_05-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "確実に成長してるわ。それも凄いスピードでね\n体力だけじゃない。ダンスも歌も",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're definitely improving. And at an incredible speed.\nAnd not just your stamina. Your dancing and singing too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_amepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "america_park",
      "startTime": 74.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_05-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "LizNoirのメンバーとしての自覚が\n出てきたってことかな。愛もこころも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I guess it means you've finally gained a sense of\nwhat it means to be a LizNoir member. Both Ai and Kokoro.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_amepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "america_park",
      "startTime": 81.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_05-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さん、葵さん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio-san‚ Aoi-san…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_amepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "america_park",
      "startTime": 84.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_05-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "当然です。私達は新生LizNoirの中心メンバー\nですから。というかもっと早く褒めてくれても――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course! We're the core members of the new LizNoir.\nOr rather‚ you could have praised us sooner――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_amepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "america_park",
      "startTime": 93.3376393636
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_amepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "america_park",
      "startTime": 95.2415267943
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_05-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "――と愛ちゃんが図々しくも言ってました～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――is what Ai-chan shamelessly said~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.2415267943,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_amepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "america_park",
      "startTime": 99.608193461
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_05-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "こころは、もう！\nせっかく褒めてもらえたのに～～っ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kokoro‚ honestly!\nYou ruined the moment!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.108193461,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_amepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "america_park",
      "startTime": 103.8748601276
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_05-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、こころの腹黒さだけは\nなかなか直らないわね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sigh It seems Kokoro's deviousness\nwon't go away so easily…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.9748601276,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_05-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "いいんじゃないかな？\nあれも彼女の個性だよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's fine‚ isn't it?\nThat's part of her personality.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.6415267943,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_amepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "america_park",
      "startTime": 113.308193461
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_05-kkr006.m4a",
      "text": "腹黒キャラなんて酷いです～。こころはみんなの\nアイドルですよ？　えいっ、アイドルスマイル！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A devious character? That's mean~. Kokoro is everyone's\nidol‚ you know? Here‚ idol smile!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.9748601276,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_amepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "america_park",
      "startTime": 118.308193461
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_amepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "america_park",
      "startTime": 121.1748601276
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_05-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "はいはい、とっても可愛いわ\nじゃあ、本番を想定したレッスンをしましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ yes‚ you're very cute.\nNow then‚ let's start a practice session that simulates a real performance.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.3415267943,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_05-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、新フォーメーションで合わせてみよう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ let's try it with the new formation.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.7415267943,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_amepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "america_park",
      "startTime": 131.0748601276
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_05-kkr007.m4a",
      "text": "こころのアイドルスマイルが軽く\n流されてしまいました。酷いです～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My idol smile was brushed aside so easily…\nThat's mean~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.8748601276,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_amepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "america_park",
      "startTime": 136.708193461
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_05-ai006.m4a",
      "text": "こころ、今はレッスンに集中しようよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kokoro‚ let's focus on the practice for now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.708193461,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_amepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "america_park",
      "startTime": 140.1415267943
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_05-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "みんな、本番だと思って集中よ\n葵、曲の準備はいい？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone‚ focus like it's the real deal.\nAoi‚ are you ready with the music?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.508193461,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_amepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "america_park",
      "startTime": 146.208193461
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_05-aoi008.m4a",
      "text": "いいよ。といっても、スマホにスピーカーを\nくっつけただけだけどね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. Though it's just my smartphone\nconnected to a speaker.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.3748601276,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_amepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "america_park",
      "startTime": 151.308193461
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_05-kkr009.m4a",
      "text": "ううっ、ショボいですね。場所もただの広場だし\nこころ達、本当にプロなんでしょうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh‚ so lame. The venue is just a square‚ and…\nAre we really professionals?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.508193461,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_05-ai008.m4a",
      "text": "愚痴らないの。あの長瀬麻奈さんだって最初は\n路上ライブだったの！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't complain. Even the great Mana Nagase started\nwith street performances!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.408193461,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_amepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "america_park",
      "startTime": 164.3415267943
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_05-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "ええ。環境なんて関係ないわ。私達の歌と踊り\nそして観客が一人でもいれば――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. The environment doesn't matter. If we have our singing and dancing‚\nand even a single audience member――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 169.9415267943,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_amepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "america_park",
      "startTime": 173.308193461
    },
    {
