      "text": "（――それは、とても不思議な体験でした）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(――It was a truly strange experience.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 181.6284113565,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
