      "text": "（私達が歌い、踊り出すと）\n（周囲の空気が突然変わったんです）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(The moment we started singing and dancing‚)\n(the atmosphere around us suddenly changed.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 188.1284113565,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
