      "text": "（みなさん外国の方で、言葉はきっと伝わってないです）\n（でも、彼らはみんな、リズムを刻み、声を上げて――）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Everyone was a foreigner‚ so our words probably didn't get through‚)\n(but everyone was tapping their feet to the rhythm and cheering――)",
        "id": ""
