      "text": "（私は感じました。今、私達は感情を共有してるんだと）\n（LizNoirの叫びが、海を越えたんだと――）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(I felt it. Right now‚ we're sharing our feelings.)\n(LizNoir's cry has crossed the ocean――)",
        "id": ""
