      "text": "どうやら、ここの人達にも伝わったみたいだね……\n及第点かな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It seems like it got through to the people here…\nI guess it's a passing grade…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 225.3048110961,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
