      "text": "ほらやっぱり感情豊かな方がいいんですよ！\nこれからはお二人もアイドルスマイルを……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "See? I told you it's better to be full of emotion!\nFrom now on‚ you two should also try idol smiles…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 244.0714777628,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
