      "text": "歌とダンスで表現するから、僕も遠慮する",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll pass too‚ since I express myself through singing and dancing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 248.7714777628,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_amepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "america_park",
      "startTime": 252.4714777628
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_05-kkr011.m4a",
      "text": "も～、まだ分からないんですか～？\nやっぱり、こころがセンターになった方が……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Geez‚ you still don't get it?\nWouldn't it be better if Kokoro was the center…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 255.8048110961,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
