      "text": "――なんて、愛ちゃん\nいくらなんでも言い過ぎですよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Ai-chan‚\nthat's going too far~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 262.5714777628,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
