      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_05-aoi011.m4a",
      "text": "やれやれ、歌と踊りは成長しても中身の方は\nまだまだか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good grief‚ their singing and dancing have improved‚\nbut their personalities are still the same.",
