      "text": "あっ、見てらしたんですか？\n先日はお世話になりました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ you were watching?\nThank you for your help the other day.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 285.8048110961,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "オーナー",
      "speakerNameEn": "Owner",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_05/sud_vo_adv_group_liz_06_05-owner002.m4a",
      "text": "いやいや、それより僕のライブハウスで歌わないか？\n君達はきっとこっちでも話題になる。保証するよ",
      "translations": {
