      "text": "「契約内容について話がある。至急帰国しろ」\nなんて呼び付けといてこれだもんね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and he sent me a message saying‚ \"We need to talk about your contract. Return to Japan immediately.\"\nHe summons us back and then this.",
        "id": ""
