      "text": "電話やメールじゃ片付かない話……なのかしらね？\nとにかく、私が着くまで話を進めてはダメよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wonder if it's something that can't be settled over the phone or email…?\nIn any case‚ don't make any progress with the conversation until I get there.",
